description:
The Dragon is ranked 4th has amassed 1160 style points vs. her opponents and has 17 massive submissions to her name. She is 4-1 this season, and is back on track to go for the title.
Newcomer Cynthia Pendragon comes from Budapest, Hungry. However she has a much nicer disposition then the other wrestler we have from Hungry. Cynthia has done some the "fake cat fighting" that pollutes the web, and thinks that might help her. Make no mistake about Cynthia she is big, strong, and now fucked.
title: The Dragon (14-4) Pendragon (0-0)
